an operating profit of NKr64m, the best operating result in four consecutive
quarters.
Last autumn, Elkem strengthened its financial base through a NKr580m share
issue and established a NKr550m credit facility.
The group pledged to continue to reduce costs and increase productivity and
said that measures already implemented had made a substantial contribution.
