FT  29 APR 93 / UK Company News: Ptarmigan suspended at 10p
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Shares in Ptarmigan were suspended yesterday at 10p pending announcement of
an acquisition.
Last October trading in the company was suspended temporarily at 2p pending
shareholders' approval of a reorganisation. Ptarmigan announced a change in
activity with the acquisition of three engineering companies.
In the year to June 30 1992 a reduced pre-tax loss of Pounds 735,000 was
announced.
